title: LordofNFTs
author: LordofNFTs
content: I invested in the show - I get 20 free tickets and only given away 4... I'm giving 10 away if any of you guys need an extra one or have not got a ticket yet.web3expo.live - Startup Alley is cool, Ryan Carson is moderating and some of the VC's are judging.  Enter your company if you are serious, have a cool project and need to raise money.  10K investors under one roof. I'm sure the organizers would work out something with the community to give discounts on the tickets..
